    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607385848459035222)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDGkkXzXpz_text","label":"ggDGkkXzXpz_text","default":"The \"Aging Protein\" Called Progerin."},{"type":"html","id":"ggh4L4_ItMu_text","label":"ggh4L4_ItMu_text","default":"<p>Much of what you're about to hear has never been shared before outside my world-renowned clinic in Korea. And it's based on ironclad scientific research from the <strong>National Human Genome Research Institute</strong> as well as my own clinical experience as a board-certified dermatologist.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4bdRiR0_k_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg4bdRiR0_k_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img1_e9422307-3f1e-4b96-9a83-80d3c2a12059.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gghF_p8Aql__text","label":"gghF_p8Aql__text","default":"<p>Today, I'm going to share with you my brand new <strong>\"Anti-Progerin Protocol\"</strong> for transforming your aging skin and achieving the youthful appearance you deserve.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL9bdTgJ3I_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggL9bdTgJ3I_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img1_e9422307-3f1e-4b96-9a83-80d3c2a12059.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg35Ax24VrF_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg35Ax24VrF_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3bximg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2S19I0igj_text","label":"gg2S19I0igj_text","default":"<p><strong>Think most anti-aging creams work? &nbsp;THINK AGAIN:</strong> Many actually contain ingredients that INCREASE Progerin levels! Keep reading — because throughout this report, I'll shatter more 'beauty industry myths' just like this.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXQZd0QHIj_text","label":"ggXQZd0QHIj_text","default":"<p>And do you know the best part?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggATFYPy_dZ_text","label":"ggATFYPy_dZ_text","default":"<p>It's actually EASY... as long as you're prepared to stop believing several myths you've heard all your life about what actually works to make your skin look and feel younger.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG8pYyRATU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggG8pYyRATU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6Ak-Eymez_text","label":"gg6Ak-Eymez_text","default":"<p>For instance, what if I told you that standard anti-aging creams are USELESS against this aging protein – and a specific peptide called Progeline is actually FAR more effective?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtai8EW-K-_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggtai8EW-K-_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMe3An4MfD_text","label":"ggMe3An4MfD_text","default":"<p>And what if I told you that French scientists discovered this \"aging protein\" by studying children with <strong>Hutchinson-Gilford Syndrome</strong>, the \"Benjamin Button\" disease that causes rapid aging?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggk-nuQkFRK_text","label":"ggk-nuQkFRK_text","default":"<p>And what if I told you that a groundbreaking study from the <strong>Society of Cosmetic Chemists</strong> found a natural peptide that can help reduce aging Progerin levels by an astonishing 22%?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv5xjErSYQ_text","label":"ggv5xjErSYQ_text","default":"<p>These statements are all 100% true and backed by science, including research from the <strong>National Human Genome Research Institute</strong> and <strong>The Advances in Dermatology Study.</strong> While they may seem unrelated, they all work because they have to do with one part of your skin...</p>"}],
